# Fixed width splits


# Splitting cost centre & ID numbers


> Select the Emp ID (Ctrl + Shift + downarrow)


> Eg : PR00147

> PR = Cost Centre  00147 = Employee number

> Data -> Text to Column -> Fixed width -> split Em p ID

> Text -> Text -> IE 

> Text -> Text -> General 

> Finish

> It shows the cost centre emp and Id number Id in two seperate coloumns.
